  - Per-step and per-episode latency / memory profiling
  - Structured result export (JSON, CSV)
  - Extension fields for future token pruning and geometric expert

Usage:
    # With YAML config
    python scripts/eval_openvla_baseline.py --config configs/eval_openvla_baseline.yaml

    # With CLI overrides
    python scripts/eval_openvla_baseline.py \
        --model_path /path/to/openvla \
        --task_suite libero_spatial \
        --num_episodes 10 \
        --save_dir outputs/openvla_baseline_eval

    # Dry-run (no simulation needed)
    python scripts/eval_openvla_baseline.py --dry_run true --num_episodes 3
"""

